text: Kamýk may refer to the following places in the Czech Republic: * Kamýk (Litoměřice District), a village in Litoměřice District ** Kamýk Castle, a castle ruins in the village * Kamýk nad Vltavou, a village in Příbram District ** Kamýk Dam, a dam on the Vltava river in the village * Kamýk (Prague), a cadastrial area of Prague == See also == * Kamyk (disambiguation), several places in Poland
title: Kamýk
